  "text": "The lung was harvested for pathologic examination at 24 h after P25 TiO 2 exposure. Tissue pretreatments and preparation of hematoxylin and eosin (H&E) stained slices were carried out as previously described [CITATION_1] . They were evaluated by light microscopy.",
